cdata.name: Volpo
cdata.desc:
Volpo is an online platform for cryptocurrencies purchase. Itsgoal is to becomea tool for the users to buy cryptocurrencies online,using fiat.Volpousers will be able to perform transactions between their local currency and VLP tokenas well as exchange the VLP tokens for their local currency.

The VLP token is an Ethereum-based (ERC20) cryptocurrency. It is a token designed to facilitate operations within the Volpo exchange, offering advantages in a formof discounts to its users.
